descript.abstract: This feature class shows point locations for various places in interest in Deschutes County, Oregon including airports, cemeteries, fairgrounds, government buildings, community services buildings, landfills, libraries, observatories, resorts, shopping destinations, stadiums, and museums.
descript.purpose: Places of Interest in Deschutes County, Oregon.
